 {"id":"remote_compilation_helper-ngl.4","title":"Web: Add Toast Notification System","description":"## Problem
No user feedback for actions or state changes. When refresh completes or an action succeeds/fails, there's no indication. Premium apps provide toast notifications for user actions.

## Solution
Implement toast notification system using Sonner (most popular React toast library):
1. Install sonner package
2. Add Toaster provider to layout
3. Use toast() for action feedback
4. Style toasts to match dark theme

## Usage Examples
- "Data refreshed" on manual refresh
- "Worker unreachable" when status changes to error
- "Build completed" for active builds finishing
- "Connection restored" after reconnecting

## Implementation
```tsx
// web/src/app/layout.tsx
import { Toaster } from 'sonner'

<body>
  <Toaster theme="dark" position="bottom-right" />
  ...
</body>

// In components:
import { toast } from 'sonner'
toast.success('Data refreshed')
toast.error('Failed to connect to daemon')
```

## Files to Modify
- package.json - add sonner dependency
- web/src/app/layout.tsx - add Toaster
- web/src/app/page.tsx - add refresh toast
- web/src/app/workers/page.tsx - add action toasts

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Toast appears on manual refresh
- [ ] Toast shows on error recovery
- [ ] Toasts auto-dismiss after 4 seconds
- [ ] Toasts match dark theme styling
- [ ] Can dismiss toasts manually
