 {"id":"remote_compilation_helper-sce","title":"Task: Benchmark History Time-Series Chart","description":"## Overview
Implement an interactive time-series chart showing SpeedScore history over time, allowing users to visualize performance trends and identify changes.

## Background and Justification
Performance can change due to:
- Hardware degradation
- System updates
- Network changes
- Shared resource contention

Historical visualization helps identify when changes occurred and correlate with events.

## Implementation Details

### Chart Component
```tsx
interface BenchmarkHistoryChartProps {
  workerId: string;
  history: SpeedScoreHistoryEntry[];
  dateRange: [Date, Date];
  onDateRangeChange: (range: [Date, Date]) => void;
  showComponents?: boolean;
}

interface SpeedScoreHistoryEntry {
  measured_at: Date;
  total: number;
  cpu_score: number;
  memory_score: number;
  disk_score: number;
  network_score: number;
  compilation_score: number;
}
```

### Chart Features
1. **Main Line**: Total SpeedScore over time
2. **Component Lines**: Toggle individual components (CPU, Memory, etc.)
3. **Date Range Selector**: Zoom to specific time periods
4. **Hover Tooltip**: Show exact values at any point
5. **Annotations**: Mark significant events (system updates, config changes)

### Using Recharts (React-native)
```tsx
import { LineChart, Line, XAxis, YAxis, Tooltip, Legend, ResponsiveContainer, Brush } from 'recharts';

const BenchmarkHistoryChart: React.FC<BenchmarkHistoryChartProps> = ({
  history,
  showComponents = false,
}) => {
  return (
    <ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height={400}>
      <LineChart data={history}>
        <XAxis 
          dataKey="measured_at" 
          tickFormatter={(date) => format(date, 'MMM d')}
        />
        <YAxis domain={[0, 100]} />
        <Tooltip content={<CustomTooltip />} />
        <Legend />

        <Line 
          type="monotone" 
          dataKey="total" 
          stroke="#3b82f6" 
          strokeWidth={2}
          dot={{ r: 4 }}
          name="Total SpeedScore"
        />

        {showComponents && (
          <>
            <Line dataKey="cpu_score" stroke="#22c55e" name="CPU" />
            <Line dataKey="memory_score" stroke="#eab308" name="Memory" />
            <Line dataKey="disk_score" stroke="#f97316" name="Disk" />
            <Line dataKey="network_score" stroke="#8b5cf6" name="Network" />
            <Line dataKey="compilation_score" stroke="#ec4899" name="Compilation" />
          </>
        )}

        <Brush dataKey="measured_at" height={30} stroke="#8884d8" />
      </LineChart>
    </ResponsiveContainer>
  );
};
```

### Date Range Presets
```tsx
const DATE_RANGE_PRESETS = [
